From George Pavlic Subject Re Ron Francis Not to mention Francis is an incredibly nice Over Christmas break a friend of mine had a little Xmas The two of us drove to Ron's While I stayed in the car out of shyness my friend went to the door and rang the Ron answered and my friend introduced He then proceeded to invite Francis to the Ron declined because he had to watch his He then reached out and shook my friend's hand I know this isn't but I don't think Barry Bonds would be this polite in this George